{"AUTUMN":[{"def":"The third season of the year, or the season between summer and winter, often called \"the fall.","pos":""},{"def":"The harvest or fruits of autumn.","pos":""}],"AUTUMNAL":[{"def":"Of, belonging to, or peculiar to, autumn; as, an autumnal tint; produced or gathered in autumn; as, autumnal fruits; flowering in autumn; as, an autumnal plant.","pos":""},{"def":"Past the middle of life; in the third stage.","pos":""}],"AUTUNITE":[{"def":"A lemon-yellow phosphate of uranium and calcium occurring in tabular crystals with basal cleavage, and in micalike scales.","pos":""}]}